Article 16  The Headquarters will take charge of the following affairs:
* Affairs concerning the preparation of a draft of the Fundamental Plan for National Resilience and the promotion of the implementation of the plan;
* Affairs concerning general adjustments of the measures to be implemented by relevant administrative organs based on the Fundamental Plan for National Resilience;
* In addition to what is set forth in the preceding two items, affairs concerning planning, designing and general adjustments of important measures concerning National Resilience.
